#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Pabbatavagga "
msgstr "1. Mountains "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Kāyasutta "
msgstr "2. The Body "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.2:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ kāyo āhāraṭṭhitiko, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhati, anāhāro no tiṭṭhati; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, this body is sustained by food. It depends on food to continue, and without food it doesn’t continue. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:1.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, pañca nīvaraṇā āhāraṭṭhitikā, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhanti, anāhārā no tiṭṭhanti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the five hindrances are sustained by fuel. They depend on fuel to continue, and without fuel they don’t continue. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.2:2.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā kāmacchandassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā kāmacchandassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of sensual desire, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:2.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, subhanimittaṃ. "
msgstr "There is the feature of beauty. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:2.3"
msgid "Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent improper attention to that "

msgctxt "sn46.2:2.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā kāmacchandassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā kāmacchandassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of sensual desire, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn46.2:3.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā byāpādassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā byāpādassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of ill will, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:3.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, paṭighanimittaṃ. "
msgstr "There is the feature of harshness. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:3.3"
msgid "Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent improper attention to that "

msgctxt "sn46.2:3.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā byāpādassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā byāpādassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of ill will, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.65, sc4
msgctxt "sn46.2:4.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā thinamiddhassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā thinamiddhassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of dullness and drowsiness, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:4.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, arati tandi vijambhitā bhattasammado cetaso ca līnattaṃ. "
msgstr "There is discontent, sloth, yawning, sleepiness after eating, and mental sluggishness. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:4.3"
msgid "Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent improper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:4.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā thinamiddhassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā thinamiddhassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of dullness and drowsiness, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn46.2:5.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā uddhaccakukkuccassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā uddhaccakukkuccassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of restlessness and remorse, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:5.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, cetaso avūpasamo. "
msgstr "There is the unsettled mind. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:5.3"
msgid "Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent improper attention to that "

msgctxt "sn46.2:5.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā uddhaccakukkuccassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā uddhaccakukkuccassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of restlessness and remorse, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn46.2:6.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannāya vā vicikicchāya uppādāya, uppannāya vā vicikicchāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of doubt, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:6.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, vicikicchāṭṭhānīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "There are things that are grounds for doubt. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:6.3"
msgid "Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent improper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:6.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannāya vā vicikicchāya uppādāya, uppannāya vā vicikicchāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of doubt, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn46.2:7.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ kāyo āhāraṭṭhitiko, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhati, anāhāro no tiṭṭhati; "
msgstr "This body is sustained by food. It depends on food to continue, and without food it doesn’t continue. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:7.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ime pañca nīvaraṇā āhāraṭṭhitikā, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhanti, anāhārā no tiṭṭhanti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the five hindrances are sustained by fuel. They depend on fuel to continue, and without fuel they don’t continue. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn46.2:8.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ kāyo āhāraṭṭhitiko, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhati, anāhāro no tiṭṭhati; "
msgstr "This body is sustained by food. It depends on food to continue, and without food it doesn’t continue. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:8.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā āhāraṭṭhitikā, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhanti, anāhārā no tiṭṭhanti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the seven awakening factors are sustained by fuel. They depend on fuel to continue, and without fuel they don’t continue. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn46.2:9.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā satisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā satisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of mindfulness, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:9.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, satisambojjhaṅgaṭṭhānīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "There are things that are grounds for the awakening factor of mindfulness. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:9.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:9.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā satisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā satisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of mindfulness, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.66, sc10
msgctxt "sn46.2:10.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of investigation of principles, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:10.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, kusalākusalā dhammā, sāvajjānavajjā dhammā, hīnapaṇītā dhammā, kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgā dhammā. "
msgstr "There are qualities that are skillful and unskillful, blameworthy and blameless, inferior and superior, and those on the side of dark and bright. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:10.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:10.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of investigation of principles, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn46.2:11.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā vīriyasambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā vīriyasambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of energy, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

#. VAR: ārambhadhātu → ārabbhadhātu (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "sn46.2:11.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, ārambhadhātu nikkamadhātu parakkamadhātu. "
msgstr "There are the elements of initiative, persistence, and exertion. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:11.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:11.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā vīriyasambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā vīriyasambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of energy, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn46.2:12.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā pītisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā pītisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of rapture, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:12.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, pītisambojjhaṅgaṭṭhānīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "There are things that are grounds for the awakening factor of rapture. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:12.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:12.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā pītisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā pītisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of rapture, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn46.2:13.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā passaddhisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā passaddhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of tranquility, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:13.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, kāyapassaddhi, cittapassaddhi. "
msgstr "There is tranquility of the body and of the mind. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:13.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to that "

msgctxt "sn46.2:13.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā passaddhisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā passaddhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of tranquility, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "sn46.2:14.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā samādhisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā samādhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of immersion, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

#. VAR: samathanimittaṃ → samādhinimittaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn46.2:14.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, samathanimittaṃ abyagganimittaṃ. "
msgstr "There are things that are the foundation of serenity and freedom from distraction. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:14.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:14.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā samādhisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā samādhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of immersion, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.67, sc15
msgctxt "sn46.2:15.1"
msgid "Ko ca, bhikkhave, āhāro anuppannassa vā upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā? "
msgstr "And what fuels the arising of the awakening factor of equanimity, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it? "

msgctxt "sn46.2:15.2"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṭṭhānīyā dhammā. "
msgstr "There are things that are grounds for the awakening factor of equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:15.3"
msgid "Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro—"
msgstr "Frequent proper attention to them "

msgctxt "sn46.2:15.4"
msgid "ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya pāripūriyā. "
msgstr "fuels the arising of the awakening factor of equanimity, or, when it has arisen, fully develops it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "sn46.2:16.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ kāyo āhāraṭṭhitiko, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhati, anāhāro no tiṭṭhati; "
msgstr "This body is sustained by food. It depends on food to continue, and without food it doesn’t continue. "

msgctxt "sn46.2:16.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ime satta bojjhaṅgā āhāraṭṭhitikā, āhāraṃ paṭicca tiṭṭhanti, anāhārā no tiṭṭhantī”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the seven awakening factors are sustained by fuel. They depend on fuel to continue, and without fuel they don’t continue.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.2:16.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
